// This folder holds all feature modules.
// Each module gets its own sub-folder, e.g.:
//
//   modules/menu/     ← menu planner logic
//   modules/logging/  ← meal logging logic
//   modules/family/   ← family member management
//   modules/insights/ ← nutrition analytics
//
// Each module typically contains:
//   actions.js   ← server actions / API calls
//   queries.js   ← React Query hooks (useQuery, useMutation)
//   utils.js     ← module-specific helper functions
